verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> ye the <S%H8034>name<s%> of <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>; <S%H1984>Praise<s%> <S%H5650>him<s%>, O ye servants of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>,
Ye that <S%H5975>stand<s%> in the <S%H1004>house<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, In the <S%H2691>courts<s%> of the <S%H1004>house<s%> of our <S%H430>God<s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>; For <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%> is <S%H2896>good<s%>: Sing <S%H2167>praises<s%> unto his <S%H8034>name<s%>; For it is <S%H5273>pleasant<s%>.
For <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%> hath <S%H977>chosen<s%> <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> unto <S%H3478>himself<s%>, And Israel for his own <S%H5459>possession<s%>.
For I <S%H3045>know<s%> that <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is <S%H1419>great<s%>, And that our <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is above all <S%H430>gods<s%>.
Whatsoever <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> <S%H2654>pleased<s%>, that hath he <S%H6213>done<s%>, In <S%H8064>heaven<s%> and in <S%H776>earth<s%>, in the <S%H3220>seas<s%> and in all <S%H8415>deeps<s%>;

Who causeth the <S%H5387>vapors<s%> to <S%H5927>ascend<s%> from the <S%H7097>ends<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%>; Who <S%H6213>maketh<s%> <S%H1300>lightnings<s%> for the <S%H4306>rain<s%>; Who <S%H3318>bringeth<s%> forth the <S%H7307>wind<s%> out of his <S%H214>treasuries<s%>;
Who <S%H5221>smote<s%> the <S%H1060>first-born<s%> of <S%H4714>Egypt<s%>, Both of <S%H120>man<s%> and <S%H929>beast<s%>;
Who <S%H7971>sent<s%> <S%H226>signs<s%> and <S%H4159>wonders<s%> into the <S%H8432>midst<s%> of <S%H4714>thee<s%>, O Egypt, Upon <S%H6547>Pharaoh<s%>, and upon all his <S%H5650>servants<s%>;
Who <S%H5221>smote<s%> <S%H7227>many<s%> <S%H1471>nations<s%>, And <S%H2026>slew<s%> <S%H6099>mighty<s%> <S%H4428>kings<s%>,
Sihon <S%H5511><s%> <S%H4428>king<s%> of the <S%H567>Amorites<s%>, And <S%H5747>Og<s%> <S%H4428>king<s%> of <S%H1316>Bashan<s%>, And all the <S%H4467>kingdoms<s%> of <S%H3667>Canaan<s%>,
And <S%H5414>gave<s%> their <S%H776>land<s%> for a <S%H5159>heritage<s%>, A <S%H5159>heritage<s%> unto <S%H3478>Israel<s%> his <S%H5971>people<s%>.
Thy <S%H8034>name<s%>, O <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>; Thy <S%H2143>memorial<s%> <S%H3068>name<s%>, O Jehovah, throughout <S%H1755>all<s%> <S%H1755>generations<s%>.
For <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> will <S%H1777>judge<s%> his <S%H5971>people<s%>, And <S%H5162>repent<s%> himself concerning his <S%H5650>servants<s%>.
The <S%H6091>idols<s%> of the <S%H1471>nations<s%> are <S%H3701>silver<s%> and <S%H2091>gold<s%>, The <S%H4639>work<s%> of <S%H120>men<s%>'s <S%H3027>hands<s%>.
They have <S%H6310>mouths<s%>, but they <S%H1696>speak<s%> <S%H5869>not<s%>; Eyes have <S%H7200>they<s%>, but they see not;
They have <S%H241>ears<s%>, but they <S%H238>hear<s%> <S%H3426>not<s%>; Neither is there any <S%H7307>breath<s%> in their <S%H6310>mouths<s%>.
They that <S%H6213>make<s%> them shall be like unto <S%H982>them<s%>; Yea, every one that trusteth in them.
O <S%H1004>house<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%>, <S%H1288>bless<s%> ye <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>: O <S%H1004>house<s%> of <S%H175>Aaron<s%>, <S%H1288>bless<s%> ye <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>:
O <S%H1004>house<s%> of <S%H3878>Levi<s%>, <S%H1288>bless<s%> ye <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>: Ye that <S%H3373>fear<s%> <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, <S%H1288>bless<s%> ye <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>.
Blessed <S%H1288><s%> be <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> out of <S%H6726>Zion<s%>, Who <S%H7931>dwelleth<s%> at <S%H3389>Jerusalem<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>.
